      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me—the one with all the dreams and the spark—died a long time ago. now i'm just kind of... going through the motions. like a ghost inhabiting a body that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
